thread.title_full: Quality Logo Products, Inc. reviewed by Katie Rappold

author: Katie Rappold
title: Katie Rappold
text: I ordered these as a promotional item for a student organization I'm a part of, and they were more than willing to work with me to find the best design for my budget and they were made and delivered in about a week which was nuts!! I absolutely love the finished product.
